Warm Fleece Dog Coat with Hood

Keep your furry friend cozy and stylish this winter with our Warm Fleece Dog Coat. Designed for small to medium dogs and cats, this coat is perfect for breeds like French Bulldogs.

Features:

  • Material: Soft, warm fleece for ultimate comfort
  • Waterproof: Protects against rain and snow
  • Hooded Design: Offers extra warmth and style
  • Easy to Wear: Simple on and off design for hassle-free dressing
  • Size: Suitable for small to medium dogs and cats

Why Choose Our Dog Coat?

This hoodie costume not only provides warmth but also allows your pet to express their personality. Ideal for walks, outdoor activities, or just lounging at home, it combines functionality with fashion.

Care Instructions:

  1. Machine wash cold on a gentle cycle.
  2. Tumble dry low or air dry.
  3. Avoid bleach to maintain color and fabric quality.
